name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 17 – Filth Mummy

content.html:
Dear Internet, On this weeks show we talk about demonic paintings, boyfriend compatibility, and ghosts feeling your buttocks. It’s a spooky one so get on this haunted hay ride with us as we tell you some stories from the internet. We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Cast of Thrones. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
